text: Baytally () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Rasmekeyevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 445 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Kushnarenkovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Baytally
